==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: molting
<hw>molting</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>The act or process by which an
animal molts; especially, the periodic shedding of the cuticle in
arthropods or the outer skin in reptiles, or feathers in
birds.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> molt, moult, moulting, ecdysis.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Molto</ent>⟦br⟧
